laptops.LPHighlighttext1: An assortment of Accent black and Dune makes the Vostro 14 3400 visually outstanding for a professional and stylish look. Color options vary by region.At less than 1.59kg and under 20mm thin, the new and improved Vostro 14 3400 is ready to go whenever you are.
laptops.LPHighlighttexts2: The optional fingerprint reader with Windows Hello allows you to easily and securely log in with just one touch.

laptops.LPHighlighttext1: ASUS SonicMaster is a combination of hardware, software and audio tuning designed with the goal of giving you the very best audio experience.A professional-grade codec ensures precise audio encoding and decoding.
laptops.LPHighlightheader2: Keeping you productive, all day long
laptops.LPHighlighttexts2: VivoBook 15 keeps you going for longer thanks to a high-quality lithium-polymer battery for all-day computing. Integrated ASUS exclusive ASUS Battery Health Charging technology helps protect your battery from overcharging.

laptops.LPHighlighttext1: They say life is full of compromises. They say you can’t have high performance and long battery life on the same notebook.
laptops.LPHighlightheader2: Ultimate performance for gamers and creators
laptops.LPHighlighttexts2: NVIDIA’s 2nd Gen RTX architecture—with new Ray Tracing Cores, Tensor Cores, and streaming multiprocessors for a huge leap in performance. Experience the most realistic ray-traced graphics, cutting-edge new features, and the power of AI in thin and light designs.
laptops.LPHighlighttexts3: Extending its legacy of max clock speeds with zero throttling over long sessions, the latest version ups the stakes even further with an intelligent intake system,A new intelligent mode uses AI to keep the most demanding games running smoothly and lag-free, while Q Control 4.0 lets you pick between turbo-charged power or extended battery life.
laptops.LPHighlighttexts4: The Legion AI Engine is our most groundbreaking gaming solution yet. Included in the Legion 5 (15, AMD), its Auto-Optimization mode intelligently identifies your game launches and optimizes system performances with dynamic CPU/GPU power distribution.

laptops.LPHighlighttext1: Spending all-day on the move requires a large battery, and at 56Wh5 it’s capable of lasting for up to 17 hours6. In cases of emergency it can also be fast charged to provide 4-hours of use for just 30 minutes charge-time7.
laptops.LPHighlighttexts2: Modern laptop users demand plenty of storage for audio and video files and plenty of memory to play them efficiently. This Swift 3 comes with a maximum of 1TB PCIe Gen 3x4 SSD, and up to 16GB LPDDR4X RAM.
laptops.LPHighlighttexts3: With a full range of connectivity options including full function USB-C™, Thunderbolt 4 the Swift 3 is capable of quickly connecting to many state-of-the-art devices.

televisions.FirstTVcardText: Unlike LCD or conventional LED technology, OLED uses millions of self-lit pixels to give you consistent detail, even when the cinematography gets dark
televisions.SecondTVcardText: Individual self-lit pixels paired with the latest gaming features and tech give you an edge with less lag, high refresh rates, and incredibly smooth and responsive gameplay.
televisions.ThirdTVcardText: OLED Motion is technology you see, but don't notice. It's motion handling for fast movements in sports and action sequences. Kickoff returns look just as smooth at home as from 50-yard line seats, with less stuttering to slow down the big car chase
televisions.FourthTVcardText: LG OLED technology unlocks a new world of TV design with a minimalist bezel and impossibly thin profile, putting the spotlight on your content while complementing your home's interior.

televisions.Tvname: Philips 6800 32 inch HD Ready LED Smart TV
televisions.FirstTVcardText: Enjoy more of your favourite movies and TV shows without the hindrance of a black frame around the TV. A true genuine art masterpiece, which you can now own in your room.
televisions.SecondTVcardText: With this Philips Smart TV win round after round thanks to its 20 millisecond input lag. This means you will enjoy smooth gameplay and help you beat your best score.
televisions.ThirdTVcardText: You can stream your content from one screen to another, using Miracast. Share presentations, videos, apps and photos - wirelessly mirror what's on the screen of one device to another for easy viewing and access.
televisions.FourthTVcardText: With a one-button press of the remote control to launch Netflix and YouTube, this Philips TV has access to countless hours of your favourite ready-to-stream content.
televisions.FourthTVcardheader: Just one click to access your favourite content

televisions.FirstTVcardText: Experience a wide range of dynamic colours that will bring images to life.
televisions.SecondTVcardText: This Samsung UHD TV offers exceptional clarity with sharp and accurate details. Get ready to be immersed in a cinematic viewing experience.
televisions.ThirdTVcardText: Now get notifications for messages, status updates at home for the Internet of Things devices and much more right on your TV.
televisions.FourthTVcardText: You can watch your TV without any messy wires dangling on the side. The first thing to do is plugging in the cables after which you can push the cables into the embedded lines on the back. This will help you neatly organize your cables through the TV stand.
televisions.SeconfTVcardheader: See More Details with 4K UHD Resolution

televisions.FirstTVcardText: Treat your eyes to vivid imagery with a high colour range of DCI-P3 93% featuring a 20% wider colour gamut—authentic cinematic colour with the OnePlus TV Y Series.
televisions.SecondTVcardText: Intuitive and intelligent. With the Android system, you can use voice commands through Google Assistant, access a range of apps from the Play Store* and explore tailored recommendations, compiled just for you.
televisions.ThirdTVcardText: The world of smart interaction is here. Inherited from the Q1 series, you can now control your TV by simply using your phone.
televisions.FourthTVcardText: It comes with multiple ports, so you can play video games or watch your favourite series on the large screen of this TV.

televisions.FirstTVcardText: This LG Smart TV runs on WebOS and lets you enjoy your favorite shows and movies on Netflix, Amazon Prime, Disney+ Hotstar, and other OTT platforms.
televisions.SecondTVcardText: The visuals on the Full-HD display of this TV come alive with stunning details and vivid colors.
televisions.ThirdTVcardText: By launching the Cloud Photo & Video app, you can watch photos and videos on the large display of this TV.
televisions.FourthTVcardText: The built-in speakers of this TV deliver flawless, rich, and multi-dimensional audio for an immersive aural experience.

televisions.FirstTVcardText: Expand your TV Viewing experience with both built-in Google Assistant and Alexa (No external devices required). Just ask, and LG AI TV satisfies your curiosity in your interest, Offers recommendations as per your tastes and controls devices on your demand.
televisions.SecondTVcardText: Now enjoy your favourite movies & TV series on Netflix, Hotstar, Amazon Prime and many more on your LG Smart TV with WebOS.
televisions.ThirdTVcardText: You will enjoy rich, flawless, multi-dimensional audio as the built-in speakers on your TV deliver sound from all angles.
